Add the following script while making the template in the template creation in the AWS console
SO that the whenever new instance starts it will do the above things
we are using this because we are curretly at the Kubernetes level

#!/bin/bash
cd ~/asg
npm install -g pm2
export PATH=$PATH:/home/ubuntu/.nvm/versions/node/v18.20.8/bin/
pm2 start --interpreter /home/ubuntu/.nvm/versions/node/v18.20.8/bin/bun bun bin.ts